PN,30901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FCompensation payments averaging over
OL,8,F#800 are due on over 12 million mis-
OL,9,Fsold car finance deals, the Financial
OL,10,FConduct Authority (FCA) has said.
OL,12,FOn Monday, the FCA published its long-
OL,13,Fawaited compensation scheme covering
OL,14,Fthe mis-selling of car finance deals
OL,15,Fthat had secret commission payments
OL,16,Fwithin the deals.
OL,18,FThe FCA said the deals meant consumers
OL,19,Fwere denied the chance to seek a
OL,20,Fbetter deal and, in some instances,
OL,21,Fpaid more for their loan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FNikhil Rathi, chief executive of the
OL,8,FFCA, said: "We've listened to feedback
OL,9,Fto make sure the scheme is fair for
OL,10,Fconsumers and proportionate for firms.
OL,11,FIt will put #7.5 billion back into
OL,12,Fpeople's pockets.
OL,14,F"Now we need everyone to get behind it
OL,15,Fand ensure millions get their money
OL,16,Fthis year. Payouts should not be
OL,17,Fdelayed any longer, especially as
OL,18,Fhousehold bills come under greater
OL,19,Fpressure.
OL,26,@pD@LOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,F"Delivering compensation promptly also
OL,8,Fgives lenders the chance to rebuild
OL,9,Ftrust, and means we can draw a line
OL,10,Funder the past and support a healthy
OL,11,Fmotor finance market for the future."
OL,13,FHow many people are eligible for
OL,14,Fcompensation?
OL,16,FThe FCA said 12.1 million agreements
OL,17,Fmade between April 6 2007 and November
OL,18,F1 2024 are now eligible for
OL,19,Fcompensation.
OL,26,@sD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FThis is down from the 14m agreements
OL,8,Fthe FCA previously said would be
OL,9,Fcovered under the scheme.
OL,11,FHow much are people owed?
OL,13,FThe FCA said the average payout will
OL,14,Fbe #829, but this will depend heavily
OL,15,Fon the finance deal that was agreed,
OL,16,Fwhen it was agreed, and the money
OL,17,Finvolved.
OL,19,FThey said they expect 75% of eligible
OL,20,Fconsumers will make a claim, costing
OL,21,Fthe industry #7.5bn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FThe #829 figure is higher than
OL,8,Fprevious estimates the FCA published
OL,9,Fas they discussed their plans for the
OL,10,Fscheme, with the last updated putting
OL,11,Fit at #700.
OL,13,FThis is partly due to the increased
OL,14,Finterest on the repayments, which has
OL,15,Fnow been raised to a minimum of 3% per
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FPayouts are expected to begin this
OL,8,Fyear, with the FCA giving car finance
OL,9,Fcompanies until the end of August to
OL,10,Forganise the implementation of the
OL,11,Fcompensation schemes, but many will
OL,12,Fbegin sooner.
OL,14,FHow can you apply for compensation?
OL,16,FThe FCA advises that people submit a
OL,17,Fcomplaint to their lender using a
OL,18,Ftemplate letter on its website.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FThe final plan has separated the
OL,8,Fredress process into two schemes, with
OL,9,Fone relating to loans taken out after
OL,10,FApril 1 2014, and the other for those
OL,11,Fprior to this date.
OL,13,FLenders will then have to respond
OL,14,Fwithin three months of launching their
OL,15,Fcompensation scheme.
OL,17,FLenders will also be expected to reach
OL,18,Fout to those customers who have not
OL,19,Fcomplained and who may be eligible.
OL,20,FPeople will need to reply to say if
OL,21,Fthey want their case to be assessed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FCraig Tebbutt, a financial health
OL,8,Fexpert for Equifax UK, said research
OL,9,Fby his organisation found that "many
OL,10,Fconsumers don't know how to check
OL,11,Ftheir eligibility and expect the
OL,12,Fprocess to be a hassle, with old or
OL,13,Fmissing paperwork being a real
OL,14,Fbarrier".
OL,26,@qD@`OUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FMuch like the PPI scandal, the
OL,8,Fanticipation of the scheme being
OL,9,Flaunched has also seen several firms
OL,10,Fapproaching people, offering their
OL,11,Flegal services to process their
OL,12,Fcompensation claim, but the FCA has
OL,13,Fmade it clear that this is not
OL,14,Fnecessary.
OL,16,FIt warns that people could be subject
OL,17,Fto unnecessary fees if they involve
OL,18,Flegal firms, and could risk losing a
OL,19,Fportion of their compensation as a
OL,20,Fresult.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FHow did we get here?
OL,9,FMany cars are bought using car finance
OL,10,Fdeals, with around two million sold by
OL,11,Fthis method each year.
OL,13,FThese typically involve customers
OL,14,Fagreeing to pay an initial deposit and
OL,15,Fthen monthly instalments with interest
OL,16,Fpayments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FMost of the car finance deals under
OL,8,Fscrutiny involve so-called
OL,9,Fdiscretionary commission arrangements
OL,10,F(DCAs), which were stopped by
OL,11,Fregulators in 2021.
OL,13,FThis refers to arrangements whereby
OL,14,Fbrokers, including car dealers, were
OL,15,Fable to increase interest rates on car
OL,16,Floans so they could get more
OL,17,Fcommission.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FIn October last year, the Court of
OL,8,FAppeal ruled that secret commission
OL,9,Fpayments made before 2021 without the
OL,10,Fmotorist's fully informed consent were
OL,11,Funlawful.
OL,13,FHowever, two lenders, FirstRand Bank
OL,14,Fand Close Brothers, took the row to
OL,15,Fthe Supreme Court, telling a three-day
OL,16,Fhearing in April that the decision was
OL,17,Fan "egregious error".
OL,26,@yD@DOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FThe FCA also intervened in the case,
OL,8,Ftelling the UK's highest court that
OL,9,Fthe Court of Appeal ruling "goes too
OL,10,Ffar", while the three motorists
OL,11,Fopposed the challenge.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FIn August, the Supreme Court ruled in
OL,19,Ffavour of the finance companies,
OL,20,Fmostly.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774937073
OL,3,CMillions of motorists who were mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance qualify for #829
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FIt meant that the anticipated massive
OL,8,Fpayout scheme was hugely pared back
OL,9,Fand was seen as a victory for the car
OL,10,Ffinance companies and car showrooms.
OL,12,FHowever, the Supreme Court did uphold
OL,13,Fone of the complaints, saying the
OL,14,Fcustomer's relationship with the
OL,15,Ffinance company was unfair.
OL,17,FThis led to the FCA setting out the
OL,18,Fscheme that was published on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
